title: Since I Reincarnated…. - Novel Updates
tags: Childhood Friends   Demons   Male Protagonist   Monsters   Nobles   R-15   Reincarnated in Another World   Sword And Magic
author: ポリ 外丸
description:
Tanaka Ryousuke, 35-year-old single, lost his consciousness during a traffic accident and was in a different world when he woke up. Thinking that his past life was an ordinary one, he thought of doing the things that he could not do before in this life and started to travel in the world.
